    {
      "text": "Puzzle Link 2 (Japanese: つなげてポンッ！2 Hepburn: Tsunagete Pon! 2) is a 1999 Arcade-style puzzle video game for the Neo-Geo Pocket Color. Like 1998's Puzzle Link, to which it is the direct sequel, Puzzle Link 2 was developed by Yumekobo and published by SNK. The game was later re-released as part of Neo Geo Pocket Color Selection Vol. 2 in 2022.",
